---
/** Planes vitalicios (pago único orientativo). */
---

<div class="space-y-4">
  <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-2">
    <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-300 uppercase" data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeKicker">
      Vitalicio
    </p>
    <h2 class="m-0 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50" data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTitle">
      Paga una vez, mantén el acceso
    </h2>
    <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeSubtitle">
      Precios orientativos para early adopters; la facturación real se activará con la pasarela.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 lg:gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto items-stretch">
    <article
      class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-200/80 dark:border-violet-800/50 bg-linear-to-b from-violet-50/80 to-white/90 dark:from-violet-950/40 dark:to-gray-950/80 p-6 flex flex-col shadow-sm"
    >
      <div class="space-y-1 pb-4 border-b border-violet-100/80 dark:border-violet-900/50">
        <h3 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeProName">Pro vitalicio</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeProDesc">Lo mismo que Pro, sin renovaciones mientras el servicio exista.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-5">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">19,99&nbsp;€</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeOnce">pago único</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="m-0 p-0 list-none space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 flex-1">
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeProF1">Incluye mejoras mayores de la línea Pro</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeProF2">Sin cuotas mientras SkillAtlas ofrezca el plan</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="/request-access"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-violet-600 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white no-underline hover:bg-violet-700 transition-colors"
      >
        <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaPlan">Solicitar acceso</span>
      </a>
    </article>

    <article
      class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/80 p-6 flex flex-col shadow-sm"
    >
      <div class="space-y-1 pb-4 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800/80">
        <h3 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTeamName">Team vitalicio</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTeamDesc">Para equipos pequeños que quieren cerrar coste por adelantado.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="py-5">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1.5 flex-wrap">
          <span class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">49,99&nbsp;€</span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTeamUnit">/ hasta 5 seats</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTeamNote">Detalle de seats al contratar.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="m-0 p-0 list-none space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 flex-1">
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTeamF1">Prioridad en soporte y onboarding</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="shrink-0 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
          <span data-i18n="pricing.lifetimeTeamF2">Condiciones de equipo por escrito</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a
        href="/request-access"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-900 no-underline transition-colors"
      >
        <span data-i18n="pricing.ctaPlan">Solicitar acceso</span>
      </a>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
